1. open rensub.py
2. set multiple absolute path for VIDEO_FOLDERS and SUB_FOLDERS
3. set execution permission for rensub.py (chmod u+x rensub)
4. execute: ./rensub.py <Series name> <Season number> <Episode Number> <optional parameters>

Examples:
    ./rensub.py doctor 6 4 #extract matching subtitle and move in the video file folder
    ./rensub.py doctor 6 4 vlc # as above but execute vlc <path-to-video-file> (it may work with other player)
    ./rensub.py doctor 6 4 copy /media/player # as the first but copy both video and subtitle file to /media/player